      "raw_text": "Nick Brown of Newport was in the\ncity last night and tells an encourage\ning story of the mining interests\naround Newport. He is particularly\nloud in his praise of the development\non the whirlpool property. He says\nIt is only four feet through the clay\nto bedrock and that the gold is plenti-\nfull enough to be a great paying prop\nosition when an hydraulic pump is\nset to work.\n\n\nCaptain Lenoe Is one of the discov-\nerers of placer ground in this Sec\ntion. Newport people have taken up\nthe matter and will give the whole\nsection further prospecting and de-\nyelopment"
    }
  ]
